e energy storage processes of the SnO2[O]rTiO2-PGN anode are dominated by diffusion-controlled behavior but present an increased surface-controlled pseudo-capacitive percentage relative to the other control group configurations. The mechanism investigation diagram based on experimental design are illustrated in Supplementary Fig. S14.
